java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class XsdTreePanelImpl
extends AbstractXsdTreePanel

This class overides the abstract class AbstractXslTree to provide a tree representation of a XML schema, with management of marshalling of several flat files to a xml file that respects the schema

Author:
Arnaud Ceol, University of Rome "Tor Vergata", Mint group, arnaud@cbm.bio.uniroma2.it
